description: This file declares exported function prototypes for the Cert IPsec Manager component, including creator, removal, object enrollment, and initialization functions. It also contains licensing and copyright information.

methods.name: PkiCreateCertIpsecManager
methods.description: Creates an instance of the Cert IPsec Manager with container, owner, and reserved handles.

methods.name: CertIpsecMgrCreate
methods.description: Creates the Cert IPsec Manager object with specified context and handles.

methods.name: CertIpsecMgrRemove
methods.description: Removes the Cert IPsec Manager object.

methods.name: CertIpsecMgrEnrollObjects
methods.description: Enrolls necessary objects for the Cert IPsec Manager.

methods.name: CertIpsecMgrInitialize
methods.description: Initializes the Cert IPsec Manager object.
